We sketched the tree out.

00:28:05.155 --> 00:28:09.280
I kind of [? drew ?] the layout,
originally, handed it

00:28:09.280 --> 00:28:12.500
to some very talented artists,
who painted it.

00:28:12.500 --> 00:28:15.490
PETE LEPAGE: Now, when you say
painted it, because we've got

00:28:15.490 --> 00:28:17.670
a lot of different types of
folks who are watching this--

00:28:17.670 --> 00:28:20.070
some may be a little bit more
like me, who are more

00:28:20.070 --> 00:28:21.980
developer oriented.

