the pieces, you'll actually see
the actual paint brushes

00:28:56.050 --> 00:29:01.660
of the artist that digitally
painted, in Photoshop, each of

00:29:01.660 --> 00:29:07.750
the elements that we created.

00:29:07.750 --> 00:29:11.950
Because we wanted it to feel,
actually, a bit of Renaissance

00:29:11.950 --> 00:29:13.200
[INAUDIBLE].

00:29:14.970 --> 00:29:15.560
PETE LEPAGE: Cool.

