I think you broke up there at
the last little second, but I

00:29:18.570 --> 00:29:23.340
think you were saying
Renaissance paintings, and

00:29:23.340 --> 00:29:25.370
each one was hand drawn.

00:29:25.370 --> 00:29:28.570
NICOLE MCDONALD: Yeah,
I'm breaking up.

00:29:28.570 --> 00:29:30.520
PETE LEPAGE: All right, well,
hopefully this will clear up

00:29:30.520 --> 00:29:31.770
here in a second.

